    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death Harvest 是一款团队合作 VR 独立游戏，每个玩家在其中扮演一群来自幸存的波士顿战斗 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部队 —— “收割者”中的一名战士。在充满僵尸的后世界末日中为幸存营地的生存而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/77e157e14522dce5e30f3612cd6c731b.poster.avif?t=1766070779\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/77e157e14522dce5e30f3612cd6c731b.webm?t=1766070779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/77e157e14522dce5e30f3612cd6c731b.mp4?t=1766070779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Death Harvest 中你可以使用很多种不同的破坏工具。仔细考虑您的策略并对不断变化的情况</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做出反应。请记住，您的生存不是唯一目标，许多平民的生命取决于你是否完成了给定的任务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/6c43d9a97ba1024bc49bb788404927bd.poster.avif?t=1766070779\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/6c43d9a97ba1024bc49bb788404927bd.webm?t=1766070779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/6c43d9a97ba1024bc49bb788404927bd.mp4?t=1766070779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管我们是一个小工作室，由工作之余的游戏爱好者组成，但我们决定无论销售数字如何，我</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >们都将提供一个可玩的完整版本的产品。只有在您的支持下我们才能完成制作，并添加额外的</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内容到游戏中。我们希望您在体验《 Death Harvest》时玩得开心，请在我们的 Discord 服务器上告 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诉我们您喜欢或不喜欢的内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/2019ed9ff5cf88e65db6d4d43cb8fda0.poster.avif?t=1766070779\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/2019ed9ff5cf88e65db6d4d43cb8fda0.webm?t=1766070779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358600/extras/2019ed9ff5cf88e65db6d4d43cb8fda0.mp4?t=1766070779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在制作过程中，我们利用人工智能：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生成配音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些临时翻译</p></li></ul>",
